_sText:
de_kalt is a port of the official dod_kalt map from Day of Defeat: Source game.

- Now this map is adapted for plant a bomb by terrorists.

Original map description:

December 1944, Western Front. The semi-frozen city of Kalt became the place where one of the cruelest battles of the war unfolded - shootouts were everywhere: on the streets, in houses, in the sewers.
